					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The value you are using for the vertical scroll is causing attribute data to be rendered as if it were name table data (because it's larger then 239). You can set the vertical scroll to $E8 instead of $F8, and instead of the artifacts you'll see the last row of the name table up there.</div>

