				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The key to negative scrolling is that it does NOT advance from FF to 100, but rather FF to 00.  Same with 1FF advancing to 100 instead of 00.
<br />
<br />So if you are trying to intentionally show attribute tables, you may need to add 256 to the scroll value.
<br />
<br />Negative scrolling is normally something you don't want.  So calculate scrolling correctly so you don't encounter it.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Here come the fortune cookies!  Here come the fortune cookies!  They're wearing paper hats!</div>
					
