					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Yeah, keeping last 32 bytes of the attribute table cleared should fix the problem, but it will severely limit your use of background palettes in the bottom half of the screen.
<br />
<br />Another solution would be to disable background rendering for the first 8 scanlines, and only then turn it on. The difficult part is synchronizing with the PPU, something that's not so trivial when you don't have a scanline counter available.</div>

